image_analysis.description: A two-page spread from a book or magazine featuring several photographs and text related to Jeffrey Epstein. The images include Epstein with Adrianna Ross, a prison cell, Epstein with a lawyer in a courthouse, a close-up portrait of Epstein, an aerial view of a facility called 'The Stockade', a screenshot of a sex offender registry entry, and an aerial view of Little Saint James island.
image_analysis.layout: Multi-column layout with integrated photographs and captions. The left page has three images and three text blocks. The right page has four images and four text blocks.
